sql.query: SELECT a.MACHINE_OID,b.DELAY_OID,b.DELAYCLASS FROM (select * from [msmodel_rep].[dbo].MACHINE where MACHINE_OID in ($)) a LEFT JOIN (SELECT [DELAY_OID] ,P.DELAYCLASS,P.[DESCRIPTION] ,J1.NAME [DELAY_NAME] ,P.TARGET_MACHINE AS MACHINE_OID ,J2.NAME [TARGET_MACHINE] ,J3.NAME AS DELAY_CATEGORY ,DATEADD(HOUR,8,[START1_UTC]) AS START_WITA ,DATEADD(HOUR,8,[FINISH_UTC]) AS FINISH_WITA FROM [mshist_rep].[dbo].[DELAY] P LEFT JOIN [msmodel_rep].[dbo].[DELAYCLASS] J1 ON P.DELAYCLASS = J1.DELAYCLASS_OID LEFT JOIN [msmodel_rep].[dbo].[MACHINE] J2 ON P.[TARGET_MACHINE] = J2.[MACHINE_OID] LEFT JOIN [msmodel_rep].[dbo].[DELAYCATEGORY] J3 ON J1.DELAYCATEGORY = J3.DELAYCATEGORY_OID WHERE J3.NAME NOT IN ('Delay Operating') AND STATUS = 3) b on a.MACHINE_OID=b.MACHINE_OID order by a.MACHINE_OID desc
sql.label: Op

sql.query: SELECT a.MACHINE_OID,c.MACHINE_OID as ID,a.NAME FROM (select * from [msmodel_rep].[dbo].MACHINE where MACHINE_OID in ($)) a LEFT JOIN (SELECT b.MACHINE_OID FROM [msmodel_rep].[dbo].[MACHINE_ONBOARD_HARDWARE] a INNER JOIN [msmodel_rep].[dbo].[MACHINE] b ON a.OID=b.MACHINE_OID where CONFIGURATION_NAME='gps') c on c.MACHINE_OID=a.MACHINE_OID order by a.MACHINE_OID desc
sql.label: Hs
